name: Caravela Cafe And Bistro

reviews.review_text:
One of the best coffee places in Goa. Lovely food and fab service (thanks, Prashant!). We ordered the Goan breakfast and a vegan breakfast- both were delicious!

Only con is the noise from the cars when sat outside in the courtyard but not much can be done by Caravela to change that.

Overall, would definitely recommend!

Great Breakfast Place!!!
Amazing Coffee!! The best I have had!! And they use metal straws!! So eco-friendly too!! I wish they were pet friendly... But sadly they are not!!
We tried the Ros Omlette and Eggs Benedict... Both were amazing!!!

The service was excellent!!!!

One of the best Brunch/Breakfast places in Goa

I recently visited Caravela Café and Bistro and the food here is EXCEPTIONAL.

**Food:**
We ordered an American Breakfast and an English Breakfast. Cappuccino was next, no words, they were just too good. I had my American Breakfast and everything was fresh, later I got a Chocolate Cupcake, it was delicious. Even they gave a spoon along side it. Later we ordered a Bombay Sandwich. Very filling, it had tomatoes, capsicum, potatoes, cucumbers, cheese, and some onions. It was so good.
On the side was potato wedges. Perfectly crunchy and sumptuous. 10/10

**Service:**
Very fast.

**Estimated Times:**
American Breakfast with Watermelon Juice - 10-15 minutes
English Breakfast with Watermelon Juice - 10-15 minutes
Cappuccino - 5-10 minutes
Chocolate Cupcake - 1-5 minutes
Bombay Sandwich with Potato Wedges - 10-18 minutes.
Strawberry Shake - 10-16 minutes

**Atmosphere:**

Very cold, ACs everywhere, not to mention fans too! If you don’t like cold and like fans, the outside seating is for you.

Rating: 5 stars.

description:
**Caravela Cafe And Bistro: A Culinary Gem in Goa**

Nestled in the picturesque landscapes of Goa, Caravela Cafe And Bistro has captivated the taste buds of 2,017 enthusiastic diners, boasting an impressive rating of 4.6 stars. The café comes highly recommended for its delightful offerings that include a medley of pancakes (71 mentions), savory eggs benedict (30), and the vibrant goan ros omelette (21). Patrons are drawn to this charming eatery not only for its delectable breakfast options but also for a taste of authentic Goan cuisine.

**Ambiance & Design**

Stepping into Caravela Cafe And Bistro, you are greeted by a cozy and inviting atmosphere that beautifully marries modern aesthetics with rustic charm. The décor is thoughtfully curated, featuring vibrant colors and wooden elements that echo the lively spirit of Goa. The lighting is soft yet sufficient, lending a warmth to the space, whether you choose to dine inside or enjoy the fresh air in the courtyard. A couple of guests did note that the outdoor seating is occasionally disrupted by passing traffic, a minor nuance in an otherwise delightful experience. Complementing the ambiance is a selection of soft music that adds to the café's welcoming vibe, making it a perfect spot for leisurely meals.

**Menu & Culinary Experience**

The menu at Caravela Cafe And Bistro shines, particularly during breakfast hours, where culinary delights take center stage. Signature dishes like the goan breakfast and the renowned Eggs Benedict receive high praise and are portrayed vividly through customer reviews, each plate elevating the dining experience. The reviews highlight the freshness of ingredients and the thoughtful presentation, making the food not only tasteful but a feast for the eyes as well.

One food lover shared her experience of indulging in an American Breakfast, complemented by a rich, frothy cappuccino and a moist chocolate cupcake—a combination both visually appealing and scrumptiously satisfying. Guest preferences also extend to delightful vegetarian options, a testament to the café's inclusive menu.

**Customer Experience & Service**

The service at Caravela Cafe And Bistro consistently receives raving reviews, with many diners complimenting the friendliness and efficiency of the staff, particularly an individual named Prashant who appears to be a standout. The turnaround for meals is commendably quick, with patrons reporting timings that allow for a seamless flow from breakfast to dessert. However, a few guests expressed a desire for the café to become pet-friendly, indicating its growing popularity among locals and travelers alike.

**Popularity & Reviews**

The café's appeal extends beyond its sumptuous menu; it has garnered a loyal following on social media, where food enthusiasts frequently share snapshots of their gastronomic adventures. Many reviews encapsulate the warm and delightful experiences shared within the café, elevating its reputation as one of the best breakfast spots in Goa. Patron endorsements, alongside vibrant visuals shared online, paint a picture of a bustling café filled with laughter, clinking of coffee cups, and the aromas of freshly prepared cuisine.

**Utilizing Visual Content**

Customer-shared photos echo the vibrant stories told in the reviews. For instance, images of exquisite dishes like the Ros omelette and pancakes show them plated to perfection, highlighting the café's attention to detail in both presentation and flavor. Captivating snapshots also capture the inviting ambiance, where décor harmoniously complements the culinary artistry. The visuals embody the essence of what makes Caravela a go-to destination for breakfast lovers and food enthusiasts alike.

In conclusion, Caravela Cafe And Bistro not only serves great food but also fosters a warm and inviting community space that resonates with both locals and tourists. Its combination of delicious meals, cozy vibe, and attentive service makes it a must-visit location on your next trip to Goa. Whether you're in for a quick coffee or a leisurely breakfast feast, Caravela is ready to deliver an unforgettable dining experience.
